    "en": {
      "title": "Bad act of women of Jaffna",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna Police arrested two women who were hiding in an abandoned house in Pommaiwely area yesterday (29) night and seized 2 grams of drugs from them.",
        "Based on the confidential information received by the police, the police rushed to the spot and arrested two women who were involved in drug use.",
        "The police said that both the arrested women are 28 and 29 years old, and they have been detained at the police station and further investigations are being carried out. (R)"
      ],
